<h3 align="center">Back Sides</h3>
Both designs show concentric calendar circles (the excentric circles are also available,
but not for the wooden instruments). The left side instrument is of a more modern design,
the big diagram in the center is the equation of time in high resolution, around it, in the lower half,
is a squashed Shadow Square as shown by G. v. Peuerbach.
The right side instrument features the classical elements: Shadow Square, Unequal Hours diagram,
and also a ring with equation of time with less resolution.

